TextData.SourceString: Has gone its whole life without lifting a finger, driven purely by primal instinct.
TextData.LocalizedString: Has gone its whole life without lifting a finger, driven purely by primal instinct.

TextData.SourceString: Drifted from herd to herd, never managing to stay in one place for long.
TextData.LocalizedString: Drifted from herd to herd, never managing to stay in one place for long.

TextData.SourceString: Spent its life solo, only now beginning to understand the importance of friends.
TextData.LocalizedString: Spent its life solo, only now beginning to understand the importance of friends.

TextData.SourceString: A born adventurer, traveled the world since it was little.
TextData.LocalizedString: A born adventurer, traveled the world since it was little.

TextData.SourceString: Former slacker, has finally begun to get its act together.
TextData.LocalizedString: Former slacker, has finally begun to get its act together.

TextData.SourceString: Having lived a laid-back life in a peaceful place, it's not well-versed in battle.
TextData.LocalizedString: Having lived a laid-back life in a peaceful place, it's not well-versed in battle.

TextData.SourceString: Once famed as a warrior in its youth, it now seeks a quiet life.
TextData.LocalizedString: Once famed as a warrior in its youth, it now seeks a quiet life.

TextData.SourceString: A natural troublemaker, driven by boundless youthful curiosity.
TextData.LocalizedString: A natural troublemaker, driven by boundless youthful curiosity.

TextData.SourceString: Used to lead a herd until one day, it cast everything aside for freedom.
TextData.LocalizedString: Used to lead a herd until one day, it cast everything aside for freedom.

TextData.SourceString: Though it used to be in the service of nobility, it now shows no sign of its former station.
TextData.LocalizedString: Though it used to be in the service of nobility, it now shows no sign of its former station.

TextData.SourceString: It was raised among many others, and thrives on coordination and group effort.
TextData.LocalizedString: It was raised among many others, and thrives on coordination and group effort.

TextData.SourceString: Once deeply shaken by failure, it's now forging ahead with renewed purpose.
TextData.LocalizedString: Once deeply shaken by failure, it's now forging ahead with renewed purpose.

TextData.SourceString: Obsessed with eating, it chases the gourmet life with single-minded passion.
TextData.LocalizedString: Obsessed with eating, it chases the gourmet life with single-minded passion.

TextData.SourceString: Tired of fleeing, it has finally decided to stand its ground.
TextData.LocalizedString: Tired of fleeing, it has finally decided to stand its ground.

TextData.SourceString: A veil of secrecy surrounds its past, known to none.
TextData.LocalizedString: A veil of secrecy surrounds its past, known to none.

TextData.SourceString: Has dozed through most of its life, driven by an endless love of sleep.
TextData.LocalizedString: Has dozed through most of its life, driven by an endless love of sleep.

TextData.SourceString: Not a fan of labor, but puts in surprising effort when asked.
TextData.LocalizedString: Not a fan of labor, but puts in surprising effort when asked.

TextData.SourceString: Finds purpose in looking after the group and being there for everyone.
TextData.LocalizedString: Finds purpose in looking after the group and being there for everyone.

TextData.SourceString: Once celebrated for its combat prowess, it now wanders with no ties.
TextData.LocalizedString: Once celebrated for its combat prowess, it now wanders with no ties.

TextData.SourceString: A traveler from birth, it has long forgotten its homeland.
TextData.LocalizedString: A traveler from birth, it has long forgotten its homeland.

TextData.SourceString: Convinced itself that being unremarkable is what makes it unique.
TextData.LocalizedString: Convinced itself that being unremarkable is what makes it unique.

TextData.SourceString: Its fixation on dieting led it to reject the very idea of eating.
TextData.LocalizedString: Its fixation on dieting led it to reject the very idea of eating.

TextData.SourceString: Too thick-skinned for even a syringe to pierce.
TextData.LocalizedString: Too thick-skinned for even a syringe to pierce.

TextData.SourceString: The kind who finishes one job only to be handed three more.
TextData.LocalizedString: The kind who finishes one job only to be handed three more.

TextData.SourceString: Finds pleasure in brute force and watching its enemies quake with fear.
TextData.LocalizedString: Finds pleasure in brute force and watching its enemies quake with fear.

TextData.SourceString: So fast you can barely see it move.
TextData.LocalizedString: So fast you can barely see it move.

TextData.SourceString: Its mental fortitude is so extreme that neither insults nor praise will phase it.
TextData.LocalizedString: Its mental fortitude is so extreme that neither insults nor praise will phase it.

TextData.SourceString: Has a long track record of shedding weight only to gain it all back just as quickly.
TextData.LocalizedString: Has a long track record of shedding weight only to gain it all back just as quickly.

TextData.SourceString: Loves pumping iron and never misses a chance to flex its muscles.
TextData.LocalizedString: Loves pumping iron and never misses a chance to flex its muscles.

TextData.SourceString: Born with natural grace, it shines no matter where it goes.
TextData.LocalizedString: Born with natural grace, it shines no matter where it goes.

TextData.SourceString: Takes pride in meticulous work and accepts nothing less than perfection.
TextData.LocalizedString: Takes pride in meticulous work and accepts nothing less than perfection.

TextData.SourceString: Wild and aggressive. It proudly claims to have never lost a single fight.
TextData.LocalizedString: Wild and aggressive. It proudly claims to have never lost a single fight.

TextData.SourceString: Thinking's not its strong suit, so it lets its strength do the talking.
TextData.LocalizedString: Thinking's not its strong suit, so it lets its strength do the talking.

TextData.SourceString: A rolling stone, restless and aimless.
TextData.LocalizedString: A rolling stone, restless and aimless.

TextData.SourceString: The life of the battlefield, always boosting morale with its enthusiasm.
TextData.LocalizedString: The life of the battlefield, always boosting morale with its enthusiasm.

TextData.SourceString: A gifted strategist who prioritizes defense and puts everyone at ease.
TextData.LocalizedString: A gifted strategist who prioritizes defense and puts everyone at ease.

TextData.SourceString: Just being near this Pal somehow fills you with motivation.
TextData.LocalizedString: Just being near this Pal somehow fills you with motivation.

TextData.SourceString: Digging is its hobby; it treasures every pebble like a rare gem.
TextData.LocalizedString: Digging is its hobby; it treasures every pebble like a rare gem.

TextData.SourceString: Treats every tree like its own mortal enemy.
TextData.LocalizedString: Treats every tree like its own mortal enemy.

TextData.SourceString: Oddly nocturnal and fixated on anything with the color red.
TextData.LocalizedString: Oddly nocturnal and fixated on anything with the color red.

TextData.SourceString: Has a gift for bonding with others, but tends to overdo it when it comes to physical affection.
TextData.LocalizedString: Has a gift for bonding with others, but tends to overdo it when it comes to physical affection.

TextData.SourceString: Boasts that it can keep working for days on end without rest.
TextData.LocalizedString: Boasts that it can keep working for days on end without rest.

TextData.SourceString: Can work all day without breaking a sweat and resents being told to rest.
TextData.LocalizedString: Can work all day without breaking a sweat and resents being told to rest.

TextData.SourceString: Even-keeled and indifferent, it always keeps a cool head.
TextData.LocalizedString: Even-keeled and indifferent, it always keeps a cool head.

TextData.SourceString: A total workaholic that gets restless when it's not on its daily grind.
TextData.LocalizedString: A total workaholic that gets restless when it's not on its daily grind.

TextData.SourceString: A light eater who always judges others' hearty appetites.
TextData.LocalizedString: A light eater who always judges others' hearty appetites.

TextData.SourceString: Has skin so thick that it puts even <characterName id=|LazyCatfish|/> to shame.
TextData.LocalizedString: Has skin so thick that it puts even <characterName id=|LazyCatfish|/> to shame.

TextData.SourceString: These days, it takes more than a little pain to feel satisfied.
TextData.LocalizedString: These days, it takes more than a little pain to feel satisfied.

TextData.SourceString: Always brags that it never gets distracted...which is, ironically, a distraction in itself.
TextData.LocalizedString: Always brags that it never gets distracted...which is, ironically, a distraction in itself.

TextData.SourceString: Can't help getting fired up whenever it sees flames.
TextData.LocalizedString: Can't help getting fired up whenever it sees flames.

TextData.SourceString: Totally the type to act out and splash around in the bath.
TextData.LocalizedString: Totally the type to act out and splash around in the bath.

TextData.SourceString: Because it loves all things electric, it has a strange fondness for electronic devices.
TextData.LocalizedString: Because it loves all things electric, it has a strange fondness for electronic devices.

TextData.SourceString: Finds comfort in nature and has a fondness for the smell of greenery.
TextData.LocalizedString: Finds comfort in nature and has a fondness for the smell of greenery.

TextData.SourceString: Keeps its emotions hidden, making it hard to read.
TextData.LocalizedString: Keeps its emotions hidden, making it hard to read.

TextData.SourceString: Gains energy simply by being on solid ground. No one knows why.
TextData.LocalizedString: Gains energy simply by being on solid ground. No one knows why.

TextData.SourceString: Truly thrives after sunset, a classic creature of the night.
TextData.LocalizedString: Truly thrives after sunset, a classic creature of the night.

TextData.SourceString: One hundred percent sure it's a dragon, no questions asked.
TextData.LocalizedString: One hundred percent sure it's a dragon, no questions asked.

TextData.SourceString: Believes it's unique, though it can't quite articulate how.
TextData.LocalizedString: Believes it's unique, though it can't quite articulate how.

TextData.SourceString: Loves the sun and proudly boasts UV-resistant skin.
TextData.LocalizedString: Loves the sun and proudly boasts UV-resistant skin.

TextData.SourceString: Absolutely refuses to get wet, turning sour the second raindrops begin to fall.
TextData.LocalizedString: Absolutely refuses to get wet, turning sour the second raindrops begin to fall.

TextData.SourceString: Seems to have lived a life untouched by static electricity.
TextData.LocalizedString: Seems to have lived a life untouched by static electricity.

TextData.SourceString: Has such a strong aversion to plants that its territory is completely free of weeds.
TextData.LocalizedString: Has such a strong aversion to plants that its territory is completely free of weeds.

TextData.SourceString: Hates the cold and is always on the lookout for warm spots.
TextData.LocalizedString: Hates the cold and is always on the lookout for warm spots.

TextData.SourceString: Has a rock-solid disposition, unshaken by even the most violent quakes.
TextData.LocalizedString: Has a rock-solid disposition, unshaken by even the most violent quakes.

TextData.SourceString: Their endless optimism can be a bit much for those around them.
TextData.LocalizedString: Their endless optimism can be a bit much for those around them.

TextData.SourceString: Thanks to a deep hatred of dragons, it knows just what to do in case of an attack.
TextData.LocalizedString: Thanks to a deep hatred of dragons, it knows just what to do in case of an attack.

TextData.SourceString: Takes great pride in its fur, never skipping its meticulous daily grooming routine.
TextData.LocalizedString: Takes great pride in its fur, never skipping its meticulous daily grooming routine.

TextData.SourceString: A stickler for rules, often too inflexible for its own good.
TextData.LocalizedString: A stickler for rules, often too inflexible for its own good.

TextData.SourceString: Has a huge ego, and stroking with praise only makes it worse.
TextData.LocalizedString: Has a huge ego, and stroking with praise only makes it worse.

TextData.SourceString: The type that works simply for the sake of it.
TextData.LocalizedString: The type that works simply for the sake of it.

TextData.SourceString: Takes on all danger without a second thought. Call it bravery...or foolishness.
TextData.LocalizedString: Takes on all danger without a second thought. Call it bravery...or foolishness.

TextData.SourceString: Brawny and short-fused, it's no stranger to causing a scene.
TextData.LocalizedString: Brawny and short-fused, it's no stranger to causing a scene.

TextData.SourceString: A bit of a troublemaker that takes delight in others' confusion.
TextData.LocalizedString: A bit of a troublemaker that takes delight in others' confusion.

TextData.SourceString: Comes off as domineering, but is unexpectedly helpful when it counts.
TextData.LocalizedString: Comes off as domineering, but is unexpectedly helpful when it counts.

TextData.SourceString: Its speed makes it notoriously difficult to pin down.
TextData.LocalizedString: Its speed makes it notoriously difficult to pin down.

TextData.SourceString: Bursting with energy at night, it is often found roaming under the moon.
TextData.LocalizedString: Bursting with energy at night, it is often found roaming under the moon.

TextData.SourceString: Skilled in subduing foes without killing. An expert in the art of the near-death blow.
TextData.LocalizedString: Skilled in subduing foes without killing. An expert in the art of the near-death blow.

TextData.SourceString: Proud of its perfect health, never once having fallen sick.
TextData.LocalizedString: Proud of its perfect health, never once having fallen sick.

TextData.SourceString: Too impatient for its own good...which often backfires.
TextData.LocalizedString: Too impatient for its own good...which often backfires.

TextData.SourceString: Always believes |it'll all work out.| It might be an optimist—but it's more likely that it just doesn't think things through.
TextData.LocalizedString: Always believes |it'll all work out.| It might be an optimist—but it's more likely that it just doesn't think things through.

TextData.SourceString: Perpetually starving. Food is the only thing on its mind.
TextData.LocalizedString: Perpetually starving. Food is the only thing on its mind.

TextData.SourceString: Thanks to a stomach that defies space and time, its appetite knows no bounds.
TextData.LocalizedString: Thanks to a stomach that defies space and time, its appetite knows no bounds.

TextData.SourceString: Often underestimated due to its simple appearance.
TextData.LocalizedString: Often underestimated due to its simple appearance.

TextData.SourceString: Has a hard time with precise tasks...and it often shows.
TextData.LocalizedString: Has a hard time with precise tasks...and it often shows.

TextData.SourceString: Convinced that the only way to fail in life is by taking things too seriously.
TextData.LocalizedString: Convinced that the only way to fail in life is by taking things too seriously.

TextData.SourceString: Lives in constant fear, but hey, that's what keeps it alive.
TextData.LocalizedString: Lives in constant fear, but hey, that's what keeps it alive.

TextData.SourceString: Dislikes conflict and tends to avoid fights.
TextData.LocalizedString: Dislikes conflict and tends to avoid fights.

TextData.SourceString: Prefers the comfort of its territory and rarely ventures out.
TextData.LocalizedString: Prefers the comfort of its territory and rarely ventures out.

TextData.SourceString: Moves through life unhurried, often losing track of time.
TextData.LocalizedString: Moves through life unhurried, often losing track of time.

TextData.SourceString: Easily shaken, even by the tiniest surprises.
TextData.LocalizedString: Easily shaken, even by the tiniest surprises.

TextData.SourceString: Consumed by total despair, it wanders in search of a final resting place.
